default.text:
'Stamp'

In Referendum 209 the community voted on whether to reset the Pichiu Parachain in order to fix bugs. The underlying proposal of this Referendum has been replaced by Referendum 205. Since Referendum 205 has passed community vote already, this Referendum was superfluous.

Artist: @kseniashikh
